snippet.title: Overwatch 2 Animated Short | “Kiriko”
snippet.description:
The protector of Kanezaka strikes again. Discover the two sides of Kiriko, the loving daughter and the deadly protector.

Play #Overwatch2 for free today on Windows® PC and Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PlayStation®5, PlayStation®4, and Nintendo Switch™ consoles.
